<br>
We were raced out of Vox on the last server reset.  This is the only dragon we have ever asked for, and we only want one shot at her so that a few of our members can say they've done her once.  If your guild is planning on her, please join up with us rather than beating us to her!<br>
<br>
Time: 9PM EST<br>
Leader:  ME, Kadath Dreamfire of Valiant Crusaders<br>
Who is eligible: 45-52 Melee/wis casters, 47-52 Int Casters, Buffers as needed.  <br>
Loot:  Loot WILL follow Midnight Sun's loot rules on this page, to the letter, no exceptions!  There are some debatable items, we live with it!<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.alaska.net/qwerty/ms/dragonloot.html">www.alaska.net/qwerty/ms/dragonloot.html</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
We will be assigning someone to loot the items that are dropped before they are rolled for. The drops will be announced and items will be randomed one at a time.<br>
<br>
Please bring along 3 peridots or 30 plat for the cost of buffs. <br>
<br>
Even if you are above lvl 53 we'd still like your support for buffing and taking out the ice giants.<br>
Should mention a few other things:<br>
<br>
1. Target # of people is 30. Wont go with under 25 or so, and wont take more than 40 people in with us. If we dont get this target, and at least 4 clerics in the right range, we wont be doing this.<br>
<br>
2. There will be no exceptions to the MS loot rules unless noone of the eligible classes is present (extremely rare).<br>
<br>
3. We need high level buffers!!! If you are 56+ and a shaman, druid, chanter, or cleric we'd love to have you along. We'll take the first, highest level of each of these classes for prep, and yes, they will be eligible for loot. I'll be looking for a res stick Cleric to join us if possible.<br>
<br>
4. If you want to join us for Giants and are 53 and over, great, but please dont whine if we ask you to head outside afterwards for lag reasons. If you join us for giants but are not part of the official vox killing groups or one of the four in #3, you will not be elligible for loot, sorry.<br>
<br>
5. We are doing this for fun, and the loot is secondary. Please no whining! Expect to die and get no loot. If you live, get loot, or both you did better than you expected! =)<br>
<br>
6. If you dont know the route inside, DONT GO EXPLORING! We'll provide adequate direction, and if you have a question dont be afraid to ask!<br>
<br>
7. Pray that she's still up tonight! Meet at the Permafrost/Everfrost zone line at 9:00 and be ready to start killing Giants long before 9:30. Timezones are EASTERN, adjust for your local time as needed.<br>
<br>
8. I recommend 100 cold resist prebuffed!<br>
<br>
9. Please sign up HERE:<br>
